### Create Order
POST {{host}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "68810b23f4937423b6320df9",
  "products": [
    {
      "productId": "64ee91b0a5a1234b9c789ef0",
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ],
  "total": 3600
}

### Get All Orders
GET {{host}}/api/orders

### Get Orders by User ID
GET {{host}}/api/orders/user/68810b23f4937423b6320df9

### Get Single Order by ID
GET {{host}}/api/orders/ORDER_ID_HERE

### Delete an Order
DELETE {{host}}/api/orders/ORDER_ID_HERE
